166
00:09:08,297 --> 00:09:11,300
Or I can timeout after a certain certain
period of time.

167
00:09:11,842 --> 00:09:14,845
And this, this really avoids,

168
00:09:14,929 --> 00:09:18,182
these goroutines from sitting out there
