00:09:23,187 --> 00:09:23,729
All right.

171
00:09:23,729 --> 00:09:24,438
Another thing I

172
00:09:24,438 --> 00:09:28,109
want to do is when I set up a worker
that's handling these go routines,

173
00:09:28,401 --> 00:09:32,613
that I want to give it some context
